<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT74">
<l>patippakaiñark kāṟṟātu pāytiraiṉīrp pāḻi</l>
<l>matittaṭainta vāḷaravaṉ taṉṉai matittavaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>vallākat tēṟṟiya māmēṉi māyavaṉai</l>
<l>yallatoṉ ṟēttāteṉ nā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My tongue shall not extol anything but the large-bodied, wondrous [Lord]</l>
<l>Who, valuing the shiny snake [Sumukha]—</l>
<l rend="indent">which, not being equal to [its] chiefly enemy [Garuḍa]</l>
<l rend="indent">reached the sea of water with leaping waves, considering [it a refuge]—</l>
<l>hoisted [it] upon [Garuḍa’s own] powerful body!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
